column2: select AssetID = a.ID, TractID = t.ID , MilesMin = MIN (d.Miles) , MilesMax = MAX (d.Miles) , Miles = AVG (d.Miles) , MinutesMin = MIN (d.Minutes) , MinutesMax = MAX (d.Minutes) , Minutes = AVG (d.Minutes) , N = count (*) from optw.tamass.ASSETS a join optw.ptheta.Portland1#Assets an on a.ID = an.ID join optw.ptheta.Portland1#Drive d on an.NodeID = d.OrigNodeID or an.NodeID = d.DestNodeID join optw.ptheta.Portland1#Tracts tn on tn.NodeID = d.OrigNodeID or tn.NodeID = d.DestNodeID join optw.tamass.TRACTS t on tn.ID = t.ID where an.NodeDist < @nodedistmax and tn.NodeDist < @nodedistmax and Minutes < # group by a.ID, t.ID
